comment: /**  * Starts watcher if not already started.  */
code: /**  * Starts watcher if not already started.  */ public WatcherServiceRequestBuilder start() {     request.start().     return this. }

comment: /**  * Stops watcher if not already stopped.  */
code: /**  * Stops watcher if not already stopped.  */ public WatcherServiceRequestBuilder stop() {     request.stop().     return this. }
